desc_long								关于这款游戏							Only the Dead Survive.                    					A massive deep-space mining ship goes dark after unearthing a strange artifact on a distant planet. Engineer Isaac Clarke embarks on the repair mission, only to uncover a nightmarish blood bath  the ship's crew horribly slaughtered and infected by alien scourge. Now Isaac is cut off, trapped, and engaged in a desperate fight for survival.Strategically dismember the Necromorph enemies limb by bloody limb.                    					Zero gravity combat means terror can strike from anywhere.                    					Uncover the horrific truth of this shocking thriller.                    						
